Enclosing class:
ModelDriver.UsesPort
private class ModelDriver.UsesPort.PackIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator

Iterator that packs elements returned by a specified underlying iterator in packages of a specified size. Each package is return by the next method within an array. The elements of this array are obtained from the underlying iterator using its next iteratively.

The remove is not provided, throwing an exception if invoked.
